ABOUT
=====

This is the Arduino version of the TV B Gone.

This code was copied from http://URL, and corrected to support EU codes by
Mitch Altman, during the TVB Gone workshop held at Hacker Space Brussels (HSB):

http://hackerspace.be/Mitch_Altman's_Electronics_Workshop

